song.info:
11th @ BreakPoint 2010 - Executable Music oldschool
The tracker has been started several years ago and is still under development. It is bundled with the music as an alpha demonstration. It features variable rate instrument, SID voice and sample support.
Feel free to contact me: Zik@cpcscene.com
